affiliate-marketing-agreement.title: Affiliate Marketing Agreement
affiliate-marketing-agreement.description: Set commission terms and protect your business when working with affiliates who promote your products for a percentage of sales.

articles-of-incorporation.title: Articles Of Incorporation
articles-of-incorporation.description: Officially register your corporation with the state. Required to legally form a business corporation and protect your personal assets.

articles-of-incorporation-biz.title: Articles Of Incorporation Biz
articles-of-incorporation-biz.description: Alternative format to officially register your corporation with state authorities and establish your business as a legal entity.

bar-agreement.title: Bar Agreement
bar-agreement.description: Set terms for bar or restaurant services, including pricing, responsibilities, and expectations for events or regular service.

board-resolution.title: Board Resolution
board-resolution.description: Document important company decisions made by your board of directors, like approving budgets, hiring executives, or major business changes.

bookkeeping-services-agreement.title: Bookkeeping Services Agreement
bookkeeping-services-agreement.description: Hire an accountant or bookkeeper to manage your business finances. Covers what services they'll provide and how much you'll pay.

brand-ambassador-agreement.title: Brand Ambassador Agreement
brand-ambassador-agreement.description: Partner with someone to represent your brand at events or on social media. Sets expectations for how they'll promote your business.

business-contract.title: Business Contract
business-contract.description: General business agreement for any commercial transaction. Protects both parties and clearly defines what each side will deliver.

business-plan.title: Business Plan
business-plan.description: Professional document outlining your business goals, strategies, and financial projections. Essential for getting loans or attracting investors.

catering-agreement.title: Catering Agreement
catering-agreement.description: Hire a caterer for your event. Covers menu, pricing, setup, cleanup, and what happens if things go wrong.

commission-agreement.title: Commission Agreement
commission-agreement.description: Pay salespeople or partners based on the sales they generate. Sets commission rates and payment terms to avoid disputes.

corporate-bylaws.title: Corporate Bylaws
corporate-bylaws.description: Internal rules for how your corporation operates. Covers board meetings, voting procedures, and officer responsibilities.

endorsement-agreement.title: Endorsement Agreement
endorsement-agreement.description: Get a celebrity or influencer to officially endorse your product. Protects both parties and sets usage rights.

event-planning-contract.title: Event Planning Contract
event-planning-contract.description: Hire an event planner for your wedding, party, or corporate event. Covers timeline, budget, and responsibilities.

food-truck-agreement.title: Food Truck Agreement
food-truck-agreement.description: Rent space for your food truck or hire one for an event. Sets location, fees, and operating requirements.

government-contract-agreement.title: Government Contract Agreement
government-contract-agreement.description: Work with government agencies as a contractor. Covers compliance requirements, payments, and deliverables.

hotel-agreement.title: Hotel Agreement
hotel-agreement.description: Book accommodations for events or negotiate group rates. Protects you from cancellation fees and ensures room availability.

influencer-agreement.title: Influencer Agreement
influencer-agreement.description: Hire social media influencers to promote your brand. Sets posting requirements, payment terms, and content guidelines.

investment-agreement.title: Investment Agreement
investment-agreement.description: Raise money for your business from investors. Protects both parties and clearly defines ownership, returns, and terms.

joint-venture-agreement.title: Joint Venture Agreement
joint-venture-agreement.description: Partner with another business on a specific project. Shares costs, profits, and responsibilities while protecting both companies.

letter-of-intent.title: Letter Of Intent
letter-of-intent.description: Show serious interest in a business deal before signing the final contract. Non-binding way to outline basic terms.

limited-partnership-agreement.title: Limited Partnership Agreement
limited-partnership-agreement.description: Create a business partnership where some partners have limited liability. Perfect for investment partnerships.

marketing-agreement.title: Marketing Agreement
marketing-agreement.description: Hire a marketing agency or freelancer to promote your business. Sets goals, budgets, and performance expectations.

memorandum-of-agreement.title: Memorandum Of Agreement
memorandum-of-agreement.description: Formal agreement between organizations outlining a partnership or collaboration. More detailed than a simple handshake deal.

memorandum-of-understanding.title: Memorandum Of Understanding
memorandum-of-understanding.description: Document mutual understanding between parties before creating a formal contract. Shows commitment without legal obligation.

nonprofit-bylaws.title: Nonprofit Bylaws
nonprofit-bylaws.description: Operating rules for your nonprofit organization. Required for tax-exempt status and governs how your nonprofit operates.

operating-agreement.title: Operating Agreement
operating-agreement.description: Essential document for LLC owners that defines roles, responsibilities, profit sharing, and decision-making processes.

partnership-agreement.title: Partnership Agreement
partnership-agreement.description: Start a business with partners and avoid future conflicts. Defines ownership, responsibilities, and what happens if someone leaves.

recording-artist-agreement.title: Recording Artist Agreement
recording-artist-agreement.description: Manage or represent a musical artist. Covers royalties, creative control, and business responsibilities for both parties.

restaurant-agreement.title: Restaurant Agreement
restaurant-agreement.description: Various restaurant business agreements including supplier contracts, franchise deals, or management arrangements.

restaurant-lease.title: Restaurant Lease
restaurant-lease.description: Rent commercial space for your restaurant. Covers rent, renovations, kitchen equipment, and restaurant-specific requirements.

service-agreement.title: Service Agreement
service-agreement.description: Hire someone to provide services for your business. Clearly defines what work will be done, when, and for how much.

service-level-agreement.title: Service Level Agreement
service-level-agreement.description: Set performance standards for service providers. Ensures you get the quality and reliability you're paying for.

single-member-llc-operating-agreement.title: Single Member Llc Operating Agreement
single-member-llc-operating-agreement.description: Required document if you're the only owner of an LLC. Protects your business status and separates personal assets.

social-media-management-agreement.title: Social Media Management Agreement
social-media-management-agreement.description: Hire someone to manage your business social media accounts. Sets posting schedules, content guidelines, and responsibilities.

sponsorship-agreement.title: Sponsorship Agreement
sponsorship-agreement.description: Get sponsors for your event or team, or sponsor someone else's activities. Defines benefits, payments, and obligations.

statement-of-work.title: Statement Of Work
statement-of-work.description: Detailed description of a specific project within a larger contract. Perfect for freelancers and consultants.

talent-agreement.title: Talent Agreement
talent-agreement.description: Work with entertainers, performers, or skilled professionals. Covers performance requirements, payment, and usage rights.

talent-management-agreement.title: Talent Management Agreement
talent-management-agreement.description: Represent and manage an entertainer or professional's career. Defines commission, responsibilities, and career decisions.

tax-preparation-agreement.title: Tax Preparation Agreement
tax-preparation-agreement.description: Hire an accountant to prepare your business taxes. Protects both parties and ensures proper handling of financial information.

term-sheet.title: Term Sheet
term-sheet.description: Outline basic terms of an investment or business deal before creating the full contract. Non-binding summary of key points.

transportation-service-agreement.title: Transportation Service Agreement
transportation-service-agreement.description: Hire transportation services for your business or events. Covers schedules, pricing, insurance, and liability.

vendor-agreement.title: Vendor Agreement
vendor-agreement.description: Work with suppliers who provide goods or services to your business. Protects quality, delivery, and payment terms.

warehouse-agreement.title: Warehouse Agreement
warehouse-agreement.description: Rent warehouse space for storing inventory or equipment. Covers storage fees, access rights, and security responsibilities.
